data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 3-bedroom 2009 ranch is a rare find, perfectly situated close to town for convenience without sacrificing the tranquility of a peaceful neighborhood. The spacious living room welcomes you with abundant natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for gatherings. The well-appointed kitchen features modern appliances, ample counter space, and a convenient layout for both cooking and entertaining. The three bedrooms offer flexibility for a growing family, home office, or guest accommodations. The master suite is a true retreat, boasting comfort and privacy. Relax and unwind on the expansive patio overlooking the beautifully landscaped backyard, perfect for summer BBQs or morning coffee. With its move-in ready status, you can start enjoying the comforts of this home immediately. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite ranch yours. Schedule a showing today and experience the allure of this fantastic property close to town. Your dream home awaits!"
